      "data": {
        "title": "Challenge",
        "body": "1. Open the markdown primitive or handle binding smoke graph.\n2. Add a handle to a markdown node.\n3. Move an edge from one semantic port to another.\n4. Confirm the primitive graphs still tell a consistent story: declaration exposes, ports render, portals open.",
