      "data": {
        "title": "Checkpoint",
        "body": "You are done when you can say:\n- a declaration names the graph and exposes surfaces\n- markdown carries explanation, not graph identity\n- a port is a surface contract\n- a portal opens or consumes what a graph exposes\n- the lesson graph itself demonstrates those relationships",
